org.webcurator.domain.model.dto
Class AbstractTargetDTO

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.dto.AbstractTargetDTO

public class AbstractTargetDTO
extends java.lang.Object

This DTO represents a Target or Target Group so that they can be readily displayed on the user interface. Note that setter methods do not affect the underlying object.

Author:
bbeaumont
